                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9Xa496LFyPw" target="_blank">Ata de Presença</a></td>
                        <td>Administradores de Evento</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-eFhbUUf_L0&t=3s" target="_blank">Envio individual pelo Whatsapp</a></td>
